{"word":"H6767 - צְלָצַל - tsᵉlâtsal - tsel-aw-tsal' - Cymbal","slug":"H6767","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צְלָצַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tsᵉlâtsal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tsel-aw-tsal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cymbal"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05DC;&#x05E6;&#x05DC; - ts<sup>e</sup>la&#x0302;tsal</b> - <i>tsel-aw-tsal'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6750\">H6750</a> reduplicated; a <i>clatter</i>, that is, (abstractly) <i>whirring</i> (of wings); (concretely) a <i>cricket</i>; also a <i>harpoon</i> (as <i>rattling</i>), a <i>cymbal</i> (as <i>clanging</i>): - cymbal, locust, shadowing, spear."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4698\">H4698</a>, <a href=\"#/H4700\">H4700</a>, <a href=\"#/H6750\">H6750</a>"}]}